    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>BANKING OFFICIAL REMOVED</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By Jennifer L. Rich</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Brazil's central bank removes banking supervision director, Tereza Grossi, while prosecutors investigate her role in $900 million bailout of Banco Marka and FonteCindam in 1999 (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Brazil's central bank removed the banking supervision director, Tereza Grossi, while prosecutors investigate her role in the bailout of two banks last year. Ms. Grossi is accused of overlooking potential illegalities surrounding the $900 million bailout of Banco Marka and FonteCindam.</p>
        <p>Jennifer L. Rich (NYT)</p>
      </block>
